Subject: [PATCH] Enable Brownfield sidebar link across all pages

Brownfield engine is live and working, so switch the sidebar nav item
from a disabled 'Soon' placeholder to a real link to /brownfield in:
- app/dashboard/page.tsx
- app/project/new/page.tsx
- components/blueprint/BlueprintDetailClient.tsx
- components/knowledge-base/KnowledgeBaseClient.tsx
- components/settings/SettingsClient.tsx

Verified: tsc --noEmit clean, next build succeeds (20/20 pages),
no new lint errors introduced.
